{"tid":2208013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好想自殺，但係無勇氣","createTime":"2020-09-18T14:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T16:00:02.000Z","uid":240095,"like":14,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"remark":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。\\ 若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：\\ [url]https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline[/url]","replies":[{"pid":"2213ea52a34fb45a21eac78a2d0d9258e92a4b59","tid":2208013,"uid":240095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"日日都畀人鬧，好似冇人認同自己咁，真係好自卑，喺屋企定係邊度都成日畀人鬧。一直都好想自殺，生存真係好痛苦，好似做咩都冇人認同咁樣，每次想自殺都會有好多藉口，冇勇氣去做。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想搵人幫手，但係好似冇人幫到我，好想死，但係又好驚身邊嘅人會好唔開心，我可以點樣做"},{"pid":"d16448aaa33e164462ed42612c26c1712c502965","tid":2208013,"uid":136416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"人生的確不容易<br />\n但我會祝福你的"},{"pid":"da9d9d619df2499231d26edd89039b56fb7b352b","tid":2208013,"uid":122513,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2213ea52a34fb45a21eac78a2d0d9258e92a4b59","tid":2208013,"uid":240095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"日日都畀人鬧，好似冇人認同自己咁，真係好自卑，喺屋企定係邊度都成日畀人鬧。一直都好想自殺，生存真係好痛苦，好似做咩都冇人認同咁樣，每次想自殺都會有好多藉口，冇勇氣去做。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想搵人幫手，但係好似冇人幫到我，好想死，但係又好驚身邊嘅人會好唔開心，我可以點樣做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"&quot;或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站      <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=f0d13419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>      。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n*由2020年10月5日起，『Chat窿』服務時段將作出以下調整︰星期一至五︰下午4時 - 凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期︰下午8時- 凌晨1時<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"8eec5faa7ea19047a65af35edd5946ce7aeeb8c1","tid":2208013,"uid":223082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"點解俾人鬧先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503e8cc176eeea513173147a6b6d8f5a21d1fa3c","tid":2208013,"uid":317021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6635402d7d9f8eedb6b726ce70073b2a6750b9","tid":2208013,"uid":234640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c8d17cafc8a54f56b03f72616b8cb0232b3d92","tid":2208013,"uid":240095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0b6635402d7d9f8eedb6b726ce70073b2a6750b9","tid":2208013,"uid":234640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"加油呀，生活痛苦但係要捱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac5dfddd064a19f67d7fb21d26818b9ed8343a2","tid":2208013,"uid":234640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0c8d17cafc8a54f56b03f72616b8cb0232b3d92","tid":2208013,"uid":240095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0b6635402d7d9f8eedb6b726ce70073b2a6750b9","tid":2208013,"uid":234640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"加油呀，生活痛苦但係要捱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmo